``But what is an Operating System : The Kernel``````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````The Kernel is the only part of a running system that can directly access````
````the computers hardware``````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````It allows access to this hardware to user-space applications````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````This access is controlled by the Kernel such that it is fair````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````````
